videos.description: Temple' great hustle gets rewarded as Jake Forrester hits a floater in the lane while drawing a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Forrester’s and-1 caps Temple’s 7-0 run) 2020/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Forrester's and-1 caps Temple's 7-0 run

videos.description: Temple's Quinton Rose drives to the rim, hangs in the air and banks in a difficult contested shot.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Temple’s Rose banks in tough leaner) 2020/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Temple's Rose banks in tough leaner

videos.description: Temple's Quinton Rose misses a right-handed shot, but gets his own rebound and lays it in with his left just as time expires in the first half.
videos.headline: Rose's layup beats 1st-half buzzer

videos.description: Saddiq Bey misses a three-pointer, but Villanova gets the rebound and Collin Gillespie promptly buries his three-point attempt to put the Wildcats up 35-30.
videos.headline: Gillespie's 3 caps Nova's 9-0 run

videos.description: Justin Moore brings the ball up court, steps behind a screen and knocks down his second straight three-pointer to give Villanova a 46-32 lead over Temple.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB One-Play (Moore’s 3 pads Nova’s lead) 2020/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moore's 3 pads Nova's lead

videos.description: Temple's Quinton Rose steals Villanova's inbounds pass, but he gets rejected by the rim on his slam dunk attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Rose gets stuffed by the rim on dunk attempt) 2020/02/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rose gets stuffed by the rim on dunk attempt
